posting_body: ['Contact info:', 'Toni Hill | The Apartment Resource |', 'show contact info', '2Br/2Ba - Elegant, Modern, In The Heart of Uptown!', 'Uptown, Minneapolis, MN', '$2150/mo', 'KEY FEATURES', 'Sq Footage:', '1165 sqft.', 'Bedroom:', '2', 'Bathroom:', '2', 'Parking:', '$125/Month', 'Lease Duration:', '12-15 Months', 'Deposit:', '$250', 'Pets Policy:', 'Cats & Dogs OK', 'Laundry:', 'In Unit', 'Property Type:', 'Apartment', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Experience Uptown Living', 'In Our Minneapolis Apartments', 'Welcome to the luxury lifestyle!', 'Our Minneapolis apartments for rent bring uptown living and style like never before with garden tubs and designer lighting complemented by granite countertops and glass tile backsplashes.', 'Nestled in the heart of the City of Lakes, our Minneapolis apartment community features a resort-style pool with cabanas and a sixth-floor lounge with rooftop terrace.', 'Alongside premier shopping, dining and entertainment, our LEED-certified apartments in Minneapolis provide everything you need right outside your front door.', 'Treat yourself to the elegant lifestyle you desire and urban flair you crave in Minneapolis, MN.', 'Prices and availability are subject to change.', 'RENTAL FEATURES', 'Living room', 'Dining room', 'Walk-in closet', 'Master bath', 'Range / Oven', 'Refrigerator', 'Dishwasher', 'Microwave', 'Garbage disposal', 'Stainless steel appliances', 'Central A/C', 'Cable-ready', 'High-speed internet', 'Wired', 'Intercom system', 'Hardwood floor', 'Granite countertops', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES', 'New property', 'Elevator', 'Secured entry', 'Shared pool', 'Fitness center', 'Near transportation', 'Guest parking', 'Off-street parking', 'Covered parking', 'On-street parking', 'Contact info:', 'Toni Hill', 'The Apartment Resource', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
